title: Total Final Sales or Purchases for the United States
notes:
Series Is Presented As Three Variables--(1)--Seasonally Adjusted Data, 1921-1939 (2)--Original Data, 1939-1946 (3)--Seasonally Adjusted Data, 1946-1967. Data Refer To Gross National Product Excluding Total Inventory Change. The Data Have Been Multiplied By 4. Data Are At Annual Rate. Source: Survey Of Current Business, For 1939-1945: 1954 Supplement, National Income; For 1946: November 1958 Supplement, United States Income And Output; Survey Of Current Business July Issues From 1958 To 1963; Quarterly Tables Thereafter (Derived From The Bureau Of Census).

This NBER data series q08295b appears on the NBER website in Chapter 8 at http://www.nber.org/databases/macrohistory/contents/chapter08.html.
